{"tid":1444544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求中央提早收回香港 立即實行一國一制","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:28:23.000Z","uid":207614,"like":35,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5ad3d38ba757dc99b67e54d05f4b1d03e997c2","tid":1444544,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"而家呢班暴徒 每日係到擾民<br />\n違法堵路示威 影響市民日常生活<br />\n我予以強烈譴責<br />\n<br />\n而香港政府 作為維護中國核心價值觀既地方政府<br />\n竟然允許外國勢力係香港大肆破壞秩序<br />\n甚至有暴徒打傷警察<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 作為一個愛國愛港既市民<br />\n我強烈要求中央<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即停止一國兩制</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解除邊境管制 讓香港重返中央管治</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一國一制</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國一點都不能少</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d4c772e16f0211231015d2fa6240ceffe9529c5","tid":1444544,"uid":207614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"一國一制<br />\n中國一點都不能少"},{"pid":"19f16d441f83e8038440f05d65ff1e7f861bec0e","tid":1444544,"uid":119175,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我要攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51b0473897a93aae418332e7096000ab26f36bc","tid":1444544,"uid":207614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"有班暴徒話<br />\n你咁鐘意咪返中國<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 我要將愛國情懷全面帶入香港<br />\n<br />\n快d實行一國一制"},{"pid":"cd850990bddfb3aeb280b7a03a71be04d3f59b3d","tid":1444544,"uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:58:12.000Z","msg":"成日話要攬炒呀嘛你班垃圾暴徒<br />\n我地13億人就實現你地願望<br />\n<br />\n立即推行一國一制"},{"pid":"ff001a2111894878256f7430503057512a789955","tid":1444544,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:59: